{"tid":1114974,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"感謝Sammi原諒安仔 黃柏高：他已經痛定思痛","createTime":"2019-04-18T21:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T02:29:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"80a150df63c968fe1591210be6879bea34cd25ed","tid":1114974,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T21:50:06.000Z","msg":"許志安（安仔）背著太太鄭秀文（Sammi）與黃心穎車廂激吻，他在記者會表示後悔，哭訴斥自己是醜惡的人，最終獲Sammi原諒。<br />\n許志安的經理人黃柏高今日回應說：「好開心Sammi可以原諒安仔，畀多次機會佢，好多謝Sammi。我都好希望記者朋友可以幫手，停止一些揣測、失實嘅報導，不要再令事件發酵，再傷害到任何人。亦好希望大家同記者朋友可以畀多次機會安仔，他已經痛定思痛，時間會證明他會以行動重新做人，多謝大家。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190418/s00009/e779e8b3062b205d90d56d76e4f20ffa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190418%2Fs00009%2Fe779e8b3062b205d90d56d76e4f20ffa.jpg&h=e08b8301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190418/1555596170849/%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9Dsammi%E5%8E%9F%E8%AB%92%E5%AE%89%E4%BB%94-%E9%BB%83%E6%9F%8F%E9%AB%98-%E4%BB%96%E5%B7%B2%E7%B6%93%E7%97%9B%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%9D%E7%97%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190418%2F1555596170849%2F%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%25AC%259Dsammi%25E5%258E%259F%25E8%25AB%2592%25E5%25AE%2589%25E4%25BB%2594-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E6%259F%258F%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E4%25BB%2596%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%2597%259B%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2580%259D%25E7%2597%259B&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=78ae6425\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190418%2F1555596170849%2F%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%25AC%259Dsammi%25E5%258E%259F%25E8%25AB%2592%25E5%25AE%2589%25E4%25BB%2594-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E6%259F%258F%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E4%25BB%2596%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%2597%259B%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2580%259D%25E7%2597%259B&h=8c380e33\" target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190418/15555961708